ok of Samuel and later literature. What emerges is a fascinating portrait of an exceptional human being who, despite his many flaws, was truly beloved by God.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Apr 2020) 7aBIOGRAPHY & AUTOBIOGRAPHY / Religious.2bisacsh40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300210163423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780300210163.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aEBA_FAO